    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >麻将</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/863b82db7b32065182a2dd799c0fe494.avif?t=1731638782\" width=636 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏是以筒子（36张）、万子（36张）、索子（36张）、字牌（28张）、花牌（8张）共计144张麻将版本为基础牌组设计的。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >麻雀卡</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >麻雀卡是游戏中进行构筑的主要手段，麻雀卡有多种类型，有简单粗暴增加伤害的，有改变出牌规则的，有需要见机行事的，有让你转危为安的……但毫无例外它们的作用就是让你变强。通过各个卡牌的配合，你将使你的麻将出牌行云流水毫无破绽，轻松通关关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>下面是麻雀卡的五种分类以及部分卡牌</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基础卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >增加基础属性</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/c079062da930fc7637ffc8488c943392.avif?t=1731638782\" width=242 height=346 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/9a1aca667a9ab72d37890d8a8d914565.avif?t=1731638782\" width=242 height=346 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/8629e971e4cf97bbdc9495618ad32eb7.avif?t=1731638782\" width=242 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能力卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >出牌或攻击时的特殊能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/db3b3390d242b8f50c7c7d0582079d5b.avif?t=1731638782\" width=242 height=346 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/e9a3157e59a2c0a5fb3214126bc949d4.avif?t=1731638782\" width=242 height=346 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/74f779dc4eeb9094747ddabe12934604.avif?t=1731638782\" width=242 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >附魔卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抽取麻将时赋予麻将特殊效果</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/a8f9e143fc7cf7d1d92d5d57e1f9ffd7.avif?t=1731638782\" width=242 height=346 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/ac8ae2f0ff834f1d09e5ed117b0e064d.avif?t=1731638782\" width=242 height=346 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/fe254f8d9e11bfedd88eca7d8dea0e73.avif?t=1731638782\" width=242 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >辅助卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >辅助卡是只能装备一张的卡，有主动有被动，大部分是强大的卡牌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/41330074e99652ca80dc3e5887bce208.avif?t=1731638782\" width=242 height=346 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/23e6fd293a7ae0bffbd524850ecf3065.avif?t=1731638782\" width=242 height=346 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/211bdc38f94765cf1216237484039418.avif?t=1731638782\" width=242 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >麻将卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这种卡会给麻将池加入特殊的麻将，每种都有不同的效果或能力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/f243cc444b38230f05bed8f70709dfa2.avif?t=1731638782\" width=242 height=346 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/2b4fac98e6aa76578eb1f680b5760a8f.avif?t=1731638782\" width=242 height=346 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/e26695739cae7692cbe7f1e897d84c4a.avif?t=1731638782\" width=242 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >零食</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149940/extras/88a0ade75da041bcee8ac716b1a1449b.avif?t=1731638782\" width=310 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中还有可以实时使用的道具，称之为“零食”，零食的作用也是多种多样，但是大多数是对你的手牌进行修改和调整的，有时候合理使用“零食”会有拨云见雾，扭转战局的作用。</p>",
